Wokstation ID: R1   ****    A riveting station operates permanent connections between parts by plastic deformation of specific parts called rivets. A rivet is a cylindrical shaft with usually a head on one of its end. During the riveting operation, the rivet is placed in a hole and the tail withouth a head is  deformed so that it expands its diameter, holding the rivet in place.
